{
    "name": "Curse Devil (Phiam)",
    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Curse devils, or phiams, are constructs of Hell that exist outside the infernal hierarchy. They are forged by more powerful devils to hunt down mortals whose souls belong to Hell. When folk speak of \u201cfamily curses\u201d or \u201cdamned fates,\u201d a curse devil is often pulling strings.<br/><br/>A curse devil is 4 feet tall and weighs 80 pounds."
        }
    ],
    "html": "<i>This short fiend has mottled pink skin, clawed fingers, and green eyes. It drags a tattered scroll behind its feminine frame.</i>",
